column2: Determine mortality and longevity of lethal effects of spinosad applied to white spheres on onion maggot mortality
White spheres with different doses of spinosad were placed in the field for different times.  After period infield, spheres were placed into cages containing onion maggot and mortality monitored.
Original data received from Nault lab in December 2018, placed into tabular form in this document in May, 2019
